  <h1 id="platform-title">Platform &amp; machine surfaces</h1>
  <p class="lead">The request scope, config, and observability primitives — plus the machine surfaces every RPC is automatically exposed through. Each sub-page drives one primitive as a live, interactive demo.</p>

  <nav class="nav">
