    <li><a href="/platform/config">Config</a> — <code>env(schema)</code> typed, boot-validated config.</li>
    <li><a href="/platform/observability">Observability</a> — <code>trace()</code>, <code>health()</code>, <code>log()</code>.</li>
    <li><a href="/platform/machines">Machine surfaces</a> — <code>/openapi.json</code> + <code>/__abide/mcp</code> from the browser.</li>
